section.text:

  Section 485(l) of the Higher Education Act of 1965 (
  20 U.S.C. 1092(l)
) is amended—

subsection.text:

  Section 487A of the Higher Education Act of 1965 (
  20 U.S.C. 1094a
) is amended by striking entrance and exit interviews and inserting pre-loan and exit interviews each place the term appears.
